13:["$","article",null,{"className":"bg-slate-50 min-h-screen py-12","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Black Friday Jamaica 2026: The Complete Shopper's Prep Guide\",\"image\":[\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607083206869-4c7672e72a8a?w=800&q=80\"],\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-25T05:00:00.000Z\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-25T05:00:00.000Z\",\"author\":[{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"DealPlug Jamaica\",\"url\":\"https://dealplugjamaica.com\"}],\"description\":\"Your complete guide to Black Friday and Cyber Monday in Jamaica — including when to really order, how to avoid shipping delays, and how to calculate your true all-in cost before you buy.\"}"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://dealplugjamaica.com\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://dealplugjamaica.com/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Black Friday Jamaica 2026: The Complete Shopper's Prep Guide\",\"item\":\"https://dealplugjamaica.com/blog/black-friday-jamaica-what-to-expect\"}]}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 mb-8 flex items-center gap-2","children":[["$","$L1c",null,{"href":"/","className":"hover:text-gold transition-colors","children":"Home"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"/"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"text-slate-900 truncate max-w-xs","children":"Black Friday Jamaica 2026: The Complete Shopper's Prep Guide"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg border border-slate-100 overflow-hidden mb-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"relative h-64 md:h-96 w-full bg-slate-200","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"absolute top-6 left-6 z-10 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm text-slate-800 text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full shadow-md","children":"Events"}],["$","$L1d",null,{"src":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607083206869-4c7672e72a8a?w=800&q=80","alt":"Black Friday Jamaica 2026: The Complete Shopper's Prep Guide","fill":true,"priority":true,"sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 800px","className":"object-cover"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-8 md:p-12","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex gap-4 text-sm text-slate-500 font-medium mb-6","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-03-25T05:00:00.000Z","children":"Mar 25, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"children":"•"}],["$","span",null,{"children":["9 min"," read"]}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold font-jakarta mb-8 text-slate-900 leading-tight","children":"Black Friday Jamaica 2026: The Complete Shopper's Prep Guide"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg prose-slate max-w-none prose-headings:font-jakarta prose-headings:font-extrabold prose-a:text-green hover:prose-a:text-emerald-700","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"Black Friday and Cyber Monday are the biggest online shopping days of the year, and Jamaicans are some of the most enthusiastic participants. But without a solid strategy, you can end up overpaying, waiting months for a package, or getting hit with unexpected customs duties just before Christmas. This guide covers everything you need to know for Black Friday 2026."}],["$","h2","1",{"className":"text-2xl mt-12 mb-6","children":"The Hard Truth About Q4 Shipping to Jamaica"}],"$L1e","$L1f","$L20","$L21","$L22","$L23","$L24","$L25","$L26","$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c"]}],"$L2d"]}]]}]]}]]}]
1e:["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"Every year without fail, Jamaican freight forwarder warehouses in Miami hit a breaking point in the last two weeks of November. The volume of packages arriving from US retailers, Temu, and AliExpress sellers is so massive that what normally takes 3-4 business days to arrive in Kingston or Montego Bay stretches to 2-3 weeks. Packages ordered on Black Friday (Nov 28) can easily arrive in Jamaica in mid-to-late December — after Christmas."}]
1f:["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"Forwarders like Mailpac and ShipMe issue annual warnings about this exact problem, but shoppers ignore them every year. Plan your orders accordingly."}]
20:["$","h2","4",{"className":"text-2xl mt-12 mb-6","children":"Why 11.11 (Singles' Day) Beats Black Friday for Jamaicans"}]
21:["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"The world's largest online shopping event is not Black Friday — it is China's Singles' Day on November 11th. Platforms like AliExpress and Temu run their deepest annual discounts on this date, and the deals are consistently on par with or better than Black Friday. The massive advantage for Jamaican shoppers: you are ordering a full 17 days before the Q4 shipping crunch begins. Packages ordered on 11.11 typically arrive in Jamaica within 10-14 days, well before the Miami warehouses get overwhelmed."}]
22:["$","h2","6",{"className":"text-2xl mt-12 mb-6","children":"How to Calculate Your True All-In Cost from Jamaica"}]
23:["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"The listed price on Temu or AliExpress is just the starting point. Before committing to any purchase, calculate your true all-in cost using this formula: (Item Price in USD) + (Freight Cost in USD based on estimated weight) + (Customs Duty, if the FOB value exceeds US$100) + (GCT at 15%, if duties apply) + (Bank currency conversion, roughly 1-2%) = True All-In Cost."}]
24:["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"For example, a US$80 smartwatch shipped via a forwarder at 0.5 lbs × US$7/lb = US$3.50 freight. Total: US$83.50. No customs apply (under $100). Convert at a JMD rate of 155: J$12,942.50. Compare that to buying locally in Kingston for J$25,000 and the saving is obvious."}]
25:["$","h2","9",{"className":"text-2xl mt-12 mb-6","children":"The Pre-Black Friday Wishlist Strategy"}]
26:["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"The smartest Jamaican shoppers start building their Black Friday wishlists in September and October. Add every item you want to your AliExpress or Temu wishlist and take note of the current prices. Then install the AliPrice extension to begin tracking the price history for each item. By the time 11.11 or Black Friday arrives, you will have 6-8 weeks of pricing data and will know immediately which \"deals\" are genuinely discounted versus which ones were artificially inflated to manufacture a fake discount."}]
27:["$","h2","11",{"className":"text-2xl mt-12 mb-6","children":"Top Product Categories to Target in the Black Friday Sale"}]
28:["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"Based on historical sale performance, certain product categories consistently deliver the deepest genuine discounts during the November sales season. Electronics accessories (phone cases, charging cables, earbuds) routinely drop 60-80%. Small kitchen appliances like air fryers and electric kettles often hit their annual price floor. Fashion items — particularly activewear, casual shoes, and accessories — see large volume-based discounts. Avoid buying smartphones and branded electronics from Temu/AliExpress during these events, as these are frequently counterfeits or grey-market devices."}]
29:["$","h2","13",{"className":"text-2xl mt-12 mb-6","children":"How to Protect Yourself: Dispute Rights and Buyer Protection"}]
2a:["$","p","14",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"Both Temu and AliExpress offer formal buyer protection programmes. On AliExpress, if your item does not arrive within the guaranteed delivery window (which extends automatically if you have not received the package), you can open a formal dispute and receive a full refund — no questions asked. On Temu, the \"Temu Purchase Protection\" programme offers a refund or free replacement for items that arrive damaged, are significantly not as described, or do not arrive at all. Always pay via credit card rather than debit card when possible, as credit card chargebacks provide an additional layer of financial protection beyond the platform's own system."}]
2b:["$","h2","15",{"className":"text-2xl mt-12 mb-6","children":"The Black Friday Jamaica 2026 Countdown Checklist"}]
2c:["$","p","16",{"className":"mb-6 leading-relaxed text-slate-700 border-l-4 border-transparent hover:border-gold pl-4 transition-colors","children":"September: Build your wishlist on AliExpress and Temu. Install AliPrice. Sign up for a freight forwarder if you do not already have one. October: Record baseline prices for all wishlist items. Check for early autumn sales. November 11: Execute your core 11.11 Singles' Day orders for items you are confident about. November 28-Dec 1 (Black Friday to Cyber Monday): Use remaining budget only for items that show a genuine price drop versus the baseline you recorded in October. December: Track all packages. Use your forwarder's consolidation service to reduce the number of individual shipments."}]
2d:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100","children":["$","$L1c",null,{"href":"/#deals","className":"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-900 hover:bg-black text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold transition-all shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5","children":["Browse Deals ",["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":"true","children":"→"}]]}]}]
